<li id="cite_note-Harmon-6">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-3" title=""><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-4" title=""><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-5" title=""><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-6" title=""><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-7" title=""><sup><i><b>h</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-8" title=""><sup><i><b>i</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-9" title=""><sup><i><b>j</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-10" title=""><sup><i><b>k</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-11" title=""><sup><i><b>l</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-12" title=""><sup><i><b>m</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harmon_6-13" title=""><sup><i><b>n</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFHarmon">Harmon, Amy (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2004-12-20"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="12-20"><a href="/wiki/December_20" title="December 20">December 20</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2004" title="2004">2004</a></span>). <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2004/12/20/health/20autism.html" class="external text" title="http://www.nytimes.com/2004/12/20/health/20autism.html" rel="nofollow">"How About Not 'Curing' Us, Some Autistics Are Pleading"</a>. New York Times<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2004/12/20/health/20autism.html" class="external free" title="http://www.nytimes.com/2004/12/20/health/20autism.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.nytimes.com/2004/12/20/health/20autism.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-11-07</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp