<li id="cite_note-SanerDisease-7">^ <a href="#cite_ref-SanerDisease_7-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-SanerDisease_7-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-SanerDisease_7-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFSaner_E2007">Saner E (2007-08-07). "<a href="http://society.guardian.co.uk/health/story/0,,2143123,00.html" class="external text" title="http://society.guardian.co.uk/health/story/0,,2143123,00.html" rel="nofollow">'It is not a disease, it is a way of life'</a>". <i>The Guardian</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://society.guardian.co.uk/health/story/0,,2143123,00.html" class="external free" title="http://society.guardian.co.uk/health/story/0,,2143123,00.html" rel="nofollow">http://society.guardian.co.uk/health/story/0,,2143123,00.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-08-07</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=%27It+is+not+a+disease%2C+it+is+a+way+of+life%27&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Guardian&amp;rft.aulast=Saner+E&amp;rft.au=Saner+E&amp;rft.date=2007-08-07&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.guardian.co.uk%2Fhealth%2Fstory%2F0%2C%2C2143123%2C00.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Autism_rights_movement"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
